### NRCC Backend - User Management Tests
### Requires: Run 01-auth.http first to get tokens

### =====================================================
### 1. Get All Users (Admin only)
### =====================================================
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users?page=0&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### =====================================================
### 2. Get User by ID
### =====================================================
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users/1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### =====================================================
### 3. Search Users by Name
### =====================================================
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users/search?name=John&page=0&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### =====================================================
### 4. Get Users by Role
### =====================================================
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users/role/APPLICANT
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### =====================================================
### 5. Get Active Users
### =====================================================
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users/active?page=0&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### =====================================================
### 6. Create New User (Admin)
### =====================================================
POST http://localhost:8080/api/users
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Jane Doe",
  "email": "jane.doe@email.com",
  "password": "Jane@123456",
  "phoneNumber": "+255799999999",
  "role": "APPLICANT"
}

### =====================================================
### 7. Update User
### =====================================================
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/users/2
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Mwangi Updated",
  "phoneNumber": "+255723456780"
}

### =====================================================
### 8. Activate User
### =====================================================
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/users/2/activate
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### =====================================================
### 9. Deactivate User
### =====================================================
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/users/2/deactivate
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### =====================================================
### 10. Bulk Activate Users
### =====================================================
POST http://localhost:8080/api/users/bulk-activate
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userIds": [2, 3, 4]
}

### =====================================================
### 11. Bulk Deactivate Users
### =====================================================
POST http://localhost:8080/api/users/bulk-deactivate
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userIds": [2, 3]
}

### =====================================================
### 12. Get User Statistics
### =====================================================
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users/statistics
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### =====================================================
### 13. Delete User (Soft Delete)
### =====================================================
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/users/10
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
